[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    435[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLanguage as a hard constraint.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Step 3's OpenSearch filter clause includes [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140m{"term": {"language": patient_context["language"]}}[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, applied as a hard rule before the k-NN search. A Spanish-preference patient cannot receive English-only content through this code path. Matches the recipe's "Multilingual Is Not Optional" framing.[K
